v3.2.2 | 2013-09-06
  * udp frontend performance improvements: no longer droppping packages
  * udp now collects metrics about itself

v3.2.1 | 2013-09-05
  * adding /v1/version resource | dgvncsz0f

v3.2.0 | 2013-08-05
